title: ThisTeam HRIS
description: A comprehensive HRIS tool designed to simplify HR processes for businesses. ThisTeam helps manage payrolls, track employee performance, store documents, and record tasks efficiently. As a Full Stack Developer, I developed the backend using Django and the frontend with React, while also designing the user interface (UI) to ensure an intuitive and seamless experience for HR teams.

title: Evergreen Butterflies Website
description: A corporate website for Evergreen Butterflies, a company that provides custom software solutions and strategic business services. The site showcases their capabilities in delivering innovative tech and data-driven insights to drive growth and efficiency for businesses. I was responsible for designing the UI, coding the website using React, and deploying it via Google Cloud Platform (GCP), ensuring a responsive, user-friendly, and scalable solution.
